o dotdash dictionarycom the daily beast investopedia and match groups online dating portfolio which includes match okcupid and tinder iacs family of websites is one of the largest in the world with over two billion monthly visits across more than  countries the company is headquartered in new york city and has offices worldwide expedia inc is the largest travel company in the world with an extensive brand portfolio that includes some of the world’s leading online travel brands such as expediacom® hotelscom® hotwirecom® expedia® affiliate network egencia® elong™ and trivago® in addition to the related international points of sale the company delivers consumers value in leisure and business travel drives incremental demand and direct bookings to travel suppliers and provides advertisers the opportunity to reach a highly valuable audience of inmarket travel consumers from  to late  mr diller served as the chairman and the chief executive officer of iac since december  beginning with qvc mr diller has served as chief executive for a number of predecessor companies engaged in media and interactivity prior to the formation of iac from october  to april  mr diller served as chairman and chief executive officer of fox inc and was responsible for the creation of fox broadcasting company in addition to foxs motion picture operations before joining fox mr diller served for  years as the chairman and chief executive of paramount pictures corporation in march  in addition to paramount mr diller became president of the conglomerates newly formed entertainment and communications group which included simon  schuster inc madison square garden corporation and sega enterprises inc prior to joining paramount mr diller served as vice president of prime time television for abc entertainment mr diller serves on the board of the cocacola company he is also a member of the business council and serves on the dean’s council of the new york university tisch school of the arts the board of councilors for the school of cinematelevision at the university of southern california and the advisory board for the peter g peterson foundation next bio joey levin back all leadership overview leadership history iac cares news button scroll up leadership  iac skip to main content iac about overview leadership history iac cares news arrow     our brands apalon prevprev brand apalonnextnext brand apalon ask applications prevprev brand ask applicationsnextnext brand ask applications askcom prevprev brand askcomnextnext brand askcom citygrid prevprev brand citygridnextnext brand citygrid collegehumor prevprev brand collegehumornextnext brand collegehumor daily burn prevprev brand daily burnnextnext brand daily burn dictionarycom prevprev brand dictionarycomnextnext brand dictionarycom dotdash formerly aboutcom prevprev brand dotdash formerly aboutcomnextnext brand dotdash formerly aboutcom electus prevprev brand electusnextnext brand electus felix prevprev brand felixnextnext brand felix homeadvisor prevprev brand homeadvisornextnext brand homeadvisor investopedia prevprev brand investopedianextnext brand investopedia match group prevprev brand match groupnextnext brand match group slimware utilities prevprev brand slimware utilitiesnextnext brand slimware utilities the daily beast prevprev brand the daily beastnextnext brand the daily beast vimeo prevprev brand vimeonextnext brand vimeo arrow      media room overview news press releases press kit arrow     investor relations overview presentations quarterly earnings sec filings fundamentals myhammer meetic stock information financial information  annual meeting of stockholders analyst coverage code of ethics faqs information request contact us arrow     careers overview life at iac job listings our brand locations arrow     about iac’s family of websites is one of the largest in the world comprised of more than  brands and products our leaders leader type  any iac senior managementbusiness managementboard of directors ia